A simple crossplatform 2D multiplayer shooter.

More infromation is available in the Wiki.

How to build under Microsoft Windows, Visual Studio 2008:
  1. Run "premake4.exe vs2008"
  2. Build build\blowmorph.sln.

How to build under Ubuntu Linux:
  1. Install SDL-1.2.15
  2. Install glew
  3. Install FreeImage
  4. Install FreeType
  5. Install pugixml-1.2
  6. ./premake4 gmake
  7. cd build
  8. make

How-to compile SDL2 under linux:
  hg clone ...
  cd SDL2
  rm -r .hg
  ./autogen.sh
  ./configure
  make
  sudo make install